  "description": "This will make the Mojang Office Cape glowing eyeblossom eyes glow like how they do in game",
  "body": "# Info\nThis will make the Mojang Office Cape orange glowing eyeblossom eyes glow like how normal open eyeblossoms do in game.\n\nWarning: This resourcepack uses core shaders to make it emissive / glow. Due to this, it may not work with optifine and iris shaders. It does however work in vanilla & with sodium.\n\n# Screenshots\n### Next to a creaking\n![Example in Gallery](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/HdOx2YHC/images/f7c2a017a1af596645966237a4c1cd999fd98363.png)\n\n### Elytra Showcase\n![Cape Example in Gallery](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/HdOx2YHC/images/4285f45ee6df75f2538591e447c7101c8322be40.png)\n\n# Other\n### Want to use this with my other packs?\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/blues-core-shaders\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/IFZoFQQs/f2f1a4985a734d66f86b87bb8a122a28b3282fd4_96.webp\" alt=\"Blue's Core Shaders\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n\nThe above pack combines all of the following:\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-office-cape\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/HdOx2YHC/cf95c8b4178ded5eeaac680be4098458455c1cc4_96.webp\" alt=\"Emissive Office Cape\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-trims\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/gxUihgVw/fc96bb5326578f80b1a245ecce2555373d47cdef.png\" alt=\"Emissive Trims\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-cape-portals\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/K0psvV8X/34840719349cbcdafe8e4e78ec02c8253256ada4.png\" alt=\"Emissive Cape portals\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-twitch-cape\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/dpiEWPp1/c3315e8bbbc049400a2166d5fb218cac8047365d_96.webp\" alt=\"Emissive Twitch Cape\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/i-am-not-steve\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SxpRZYW5/d282e7848bca5aab9bc969480d200f3c09c137b6_96.webp\" alt=\"I am not steve\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>",
